{"tid":2371999,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港最新失業率升至6.6%，學者預期本港失業率或升至7%","createTime":"2021-01-19T09:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T11:01:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3fafbd910eca21ca7cb06470376a7e53baed06d8","tid":2371999,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571233-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571233-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrKgSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=513d9d20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571233-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=52e628a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571233-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n本港最新失業率升至6.6%，為16年來的高位，就業不足率則維持3.4%的水平。<br />\n<br />\n中大商學院高級講師李兆波表示，最新失業率屬意料之內，反映保就業計劃結束後的一個月的情況。對於餐飲業的失業率升至13.8%。李兆波說，年尾屬餐飲業界的黃金檔期，但受限聚令及晚市禁堂食影響，對業界打擊很大。他預期，如疫情持續，整體失業率未來有機會升至7%。<br />\n<br />\n至於失業率會否高過沙士時期，李兆波相信機會不大，除非疫情不受控，否則隨著市民稍後接種疫苗，相信疫情會緩和，失業率未必會升至沙士時的超過8%。<br />\n<br />\n李兆波建議，政府可針對受困行業如旅遊、餐飲業而設立保就業計劃，提供短期補助，但最重要仍然是盡快控制疫情，否則經濟不知可以「捱幾耐」。"},{"pid":"a63c2843e17ba60b44d944b6472fa0c19442a038","tid":2371999,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"李兆波有冇去donki行?"},{"pid":"1bceb2e8ae9eff14f510739bfafa091b5d268042","tid":2371999,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"公務員失業率=0%"},{"pid":"137b6de5f4be667c782ef0c6274f8385bf1a3b67","tid":2371999,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bceb2e8ae9eff14f510739bfafa091b5d268042","tid":2371999,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"公務員失業率=0%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:08:2